data.title: Uintah County Library
data.text:
The Duchesne Branch is being remodeled from May 6 - November 30, 2024. Its items will be unavailable from April 1 until the branch reopens. Thank you for your patience during this closure.

The Library will be closed on Monday, September 2nd, in observance of Labor Day. We will reopen on Tuesday, September 3rd, and 9:00 AM. Have a great weekend!
